# Tasks

The "Tasks" file is the active task tracking: current task details, checklists, component lists.
It contains an exhaustive checklist of all the necessary steps to do, in order, to complete the current task.

## File

`memory-bank/tasks.md`

## How to Create

When planning work, fill out the task list with sections of checklists appropriate to the complexity level of the current task.

